| Save action | ŌĆö | text CTA pattern: `text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest` |

The `gap-px bg-border-default` pattern produces 1px hairline dividers between tiles ŌĆö the grid reads as a single photographic array, not as individual cards.

### Profile Highlights & Favourites

| Pattern | Tailwind class |
