### Component 3: RLS (`company_stewards`)

**SELECT** ŌĆö admin, rowŌĆÖs `user_id`, or any steward of the same `company_id` (membership for co-stewards is evaluated via SQL helper `plano_auth_is_company_steward(company_id)` ŌĆö `SECURITY DEFINER` ŌĆö so the policy does not sub-select `company_stewards` under the same RLS rules, avoiding infinite recursion on REST reads; migration `20270839000000_feed_main_image_and_steward_rls.sql`).

